How to unschedule node ?
      --> kubectl cordon <IP Address of the Node> 
                or
      --> kubectl cordon $NodeName
      
How to schedule your nodes ?

      --> kubectl uncordon <IP Address>
                  or
      --> kubectl uncordon $NodeName
      
Want to learn are know the commands of kubectl: (A complete commands of kubernetes)
                  https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/kubectl/cheatsheet/ 
